                <h1>Prepasted vs. Peel-and-Stick Wallpaper: Key Differences</h1>
                <p>Prepasted wallpaper and peel-and-stick wallpaper serve the same purpose—adding style—but they differ in application methods. Prepasted wallpaper requires water to activate the adhesive, while peel-and-stick wallpaper has a built-in adhesive backing that allows for an easier, mess-free application and removal. Choose based on your preference!</p>
